for the last year of production of AC1,

24
00:01:11,138 --> 00:01:13,340
then moving as a game designer on AC2.

25
00:01:14,881 --> 00:01:17,684
Then for two years, I worked more at the brand level,

26
00:01:17,964 --> 00:01:19,825
overseeing a bit the entire universe.

27
00:01:20,406 --> 00:01:22,327
And I came back to the production level

28
00:01:22,347 --> 00:01:23,288
as a creative director,

29
00:01:23,928 --> 00:01:25,790
where I had the honor and privilege

30
