00:29:41,511 --> 00:29:46,512
We even added submissions in Black Flag through the website.

530
00:29:46,972 --> 00:29:49,773
So we were pretty confident that this was the way to go.

531
00:29:50,333 --> 00:29:55,134
Thing is, and I will come back later on that topic, like I

532
00:29:55,194 --> 00:29:58,395
said, the hardcore fans were really into it and enjoyed it.

533
00:29:59,186 --> 00:30:02,907
But we didn't maybe listen enough to the mass,

534
00:30:03,287 --> 00:30:06,208
to the majority of our audience.

535
00:30:07,108 --> 00:30:09,669
And so Unity, that was the following game,

536
00:30:10,509 --> 00:30:14,771
and remember, started back in 2011, after Brotherhood,

537
00:30:15,531 --> 00:30:17,512
was really meant to be the new next-gen game.

538
