00:53:21,232 --> 00:53:25,834
that way, almost, when with the co-dev is really, we are teams, you know?

976
00:53:26,315 --> 00:53:33,679
And so when you think about Origins, Sophia had the responsibility to bring all the tombs,

977
00:53:34,199 --> 00:53:40,743
all the pyramids, for example, for the entire games, plus their region, including their

