00:53:50,919 --> 00:53:52,479
So obviously we were giving feedback.

983
00:53:52,839 --> 00:53:55,420
Montreal was giving feedback with them, working on that.

984
00:53:55,460 --> 00:53:57,681
But that's their stuff.

985
00:53:57,701 --> 00:54:01,602
They developed systems specifically for that from,

