00:54:06,344 --> 00:54:09,445
I'm responsible for the overall experience.

989
00:54:10,264 --> 00:54:11,766
So I won't go into the detail.

990
00:54:11,786 --> 00:54:14,508
I'm not the game designer above the game designer.

991
00:54:14,608 --> 00:54:18,432
I'm not the artistic director above the artistic director.

992
00:54:18,793 --> 00:54:20,695
My focus is really the global experience.

993
00:54:20,735 --> 00:54:24,799
So if it's in line, if the purpose is good,

994
00:54:25,099 --> 00:54:27,521
if it fits the global vision, then do it.

995
00:54:28,282 --> 00:54:28,763
Great, thank you.

996
00:54:30,011 --> 00:54:32,513
Hi, so firstly it was a great talk, so thanks very much for that.

